{"title":"飞！——短歌两首，赠到农业生产第一线的同志","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":11,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——短歌两首，赠到农业生产第一线的同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁展翅南北飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高海阔任你飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手笔来一手锨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两翅担起山和水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根根羽毛变谷穗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞呀一步一层天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞呀，飞到金桥去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是火焰就把荒山点；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞呀，飞向第一线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是雷电就把春光催；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地之间一熔炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火箭需要铁来炼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是党的一枝箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要射向地球最高巅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠红鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你太阳的儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来自毛泽东身边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社是太阳城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里四季是春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山大山能当铁锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你挥舞阶级汗水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大泉大泉唤起风雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你来把天堂描绘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号角声声火光万点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——来呀，红鹰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天广地阔风驰电闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——来呀，春燕！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}